{"id": "1510264691673272350", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "1255343591933476987", "author_name": "n_gm0803", "author_bot": false, "content": "私もすみません\n成長素材もまだ足らないのでこの子を育てておけとかあればご助言いただけると助かります。\nランダム瓶はさっき割りましたが、交換のものも何がいいのか全然わかってませんので、併せておすすめありましたら助かります🙏", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:52:41.856000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1510264690704388256", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1332917, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510166825038516354/1510264690704388256/image.png?ex=6a33ea19&is=6a329899&hm=ea7a7c37caccb25e77bfa766e71358325cff286a9d70259694aba2a2601906fe&"}, {"id": "1510264691203768340", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 919807, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1510166825038516354/1510264691203768340/image.png?ex=6a33ea19&is=6a329899&hm=6e8d9805eee69e1abfe86e9e3afde76514d4aefb61385f45f18d2b954962b319&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510265529602932916", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "636125701510135828", "author_name": "03157", "author_bot": false, "content": "ソレールさんは何凸しといた方がいいですか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:56:01.634000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510265598763077744", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 19, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "無凸でも強いです！", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:56:18.123000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["636125701510135828"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1510265529602932916", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510265652261290045", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "欲しいのは札ですかね", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:56:30.878000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510265989152116736", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "636125701510135828", "author_name": "03157", "author_bot": false, "content": "なるほど、ちょうどピックアップされているやつですね。\nこれは何凸で実用的になりますか？\n沙耶が２凸くらいで使い物になるらしいというのは雑談で見ましたが、沙耶の札も何凸するべきですか？", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:57:51.199000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510266227946164275", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 19, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "サルバドル無凸でもいるだけでストーリー本当に楽になるのでサルバ、オルラもかなり支援性能強いのでおすすめです。恒常だとヘロットなんかは育てておいて損は無いかと", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T12:58:48.132000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1255343591933476987"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1510264691673272350", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510267112520683662", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 19, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "札は大体3凸するか完凸するかくらいですかね。でも完凸とか厳しいので3凸かなと、無凸だけでも最低限確保さえしていれば後々また凸できるし効果も全然使えるので", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T13:02:19.031000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["636125701510135828"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1510265989152116736", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510267235841736756", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "まぁ無凸か余裕あれば3凸ですかね", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T13:02:48.433000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510267415563604139", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 0, "author_id": "1421799819877290054", "author_name": "yamaiame_ql4", "author_bot": false, "content": "沙耶札は無凸だけでも強いと思います。こちらも余裕あれば3ですかね", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T13:03:31.282000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
{"id": "1510267724524425236", "channel_id": "1510166825038516354", "type": 19, "author_id": "636125701510135828", "author_name": "03157", "author_bot": false, "content": "お返事ありがとうございます。\nとりあえず確保できるように頑張ります。", "timestamp": "2026-05-30T13:04:44.944000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1421799819877290054"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1510267112520683662", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1510166825038516354", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "沙耶を活かしたい", "forum_channel_id": "1391703584755941467"}
